imdb.plot outline: Open Ended is a lifestyle series with purpose, about adventure, success and wellbeing. An exploration across the globe, where in each episode, we meet some of the worlds high achievers, have uncharted adventures and learn the keys to flourishing alongside host Scott Bidmead. At its core, Open Ended's vision is to help people flourish.
